Millabeth's Shoppe~
   This bright, airy shop is immaculately clean and its furnishings sparse yet
welcoming.  Vases of flowers are set in several places, filling the room with a
fresh scent.  It is evident that this is not a business for profit, but rather,
a labour of love for its proprietor.  Millabeth walks about the room, welcoming
strangers and greeting old friends with the same cheerful smile that
immediately sets all at ease.  Occasionally, one of her suppliers stops in to
offer the latest items for her perusal, which she pours over carefully,
commenting quietly on her selections.  Several windows in each wall catch the
slightest sunlight during the day, and a door stands open to the north.    
